name: Beverly Hills Polo Club 657BHP0544
description: The women's crossbody bag, from the company Beverly Hills Polo Club, is made of synthetic leather, processed by the Saffiano method. Saffiano leather has a textured texture due to a machine that imprints on the skin (stamping method) these characteristic lines of the skin. It has great resistance to time and dirt while its processing is completed with a layer of wax. As a result, Saffiano skin is very resistant to scratches, repels water, and is very easy to clean.
